Package: STRINGutils
Title: Additional utilities for STRINGdb
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Chia Sin",
           family = "Liew",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "c.s.liew@huskers.unl.edu")
Description: STRINGdb R package provides a convenient way to access the popular STRING
    database (https://string-db.org) from R. STRINGutils is built on top of STRINGdb 
    and provides convenient functions to get SVG file of STRING network and 
    highlight features of interest.
